{"title":"[演算法]馬可夫鏈 (Markov Chain)","date":"2020-03-08T11:22:06.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 8, 2020","L":"03/08/2020","MM-DD":"03-08"},"link":"2020/03/08/MarkovChain","tags":["JS","W3HEXSCHOOL","演算法"],"updated":"2020-06-18T16:55:49.558Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><p>…</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h1 id=\"淺談-馬可夫鏈-Markov-Chain\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/03/08/MarkovChain#淺談-馬可夫鏈-Markov-Chain\"></a>淺談 馬可夫鏈 (Markov Chain)</h1>\n<h2 id=\"原理：\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/03/08/MarkovChain#原理：\"></a>原理：</h2>\n<p><strong>馬可夫鏈</strong>（英語：<strong>Markov chain</strong>），又稱<font color=\"red\">離散時間馬可夫鏈</font>（discrete-time Markov chain，縮寫為<font color=\"blue\">DTMC</font>），因俄國數學家<strong>安德烈·馬可夫</strong>得名</p>\n<p>為狀態空間中經過從<strong>一個狀態到另一個狀態的轉換的隨機過程</strong>。</p>\n<p>該過程要求具備<font color=\"red\">「無記憶」</font>的性質：</p>\n<p>下一狀態的機率分布只能由當前狀態決定，在時間序列中它前面的事件均與之無關。</p>\n<p>這種特定類型的「無記憶性」稱作馬可夫性質。馬爾科夫鏈作為實際過程的統計模型具有許多應用。</p>\n<p><strong>接下來以故事來說明：</strong></p>\n<p>有一位新進的員工叫小楨，由於她住的地方離上班地點非常遙遠，必須一大早就騎著山豬通勤，因此常常上班遲到。</p>\n<p>因此身為她的老闆非常困擾，決定利用演算法中的<strong>馬可夫鍊</strong>來</p>\n<p><mark><em>預測小楨下個星期出勤狀況，計算發生的機率為何呢？？</em></mark></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bAEI8Z4.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><strong>下圖為小楨出勤狀態圖</strong>：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ulypSQw.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>小楨出勤有2種狀態分別是<strong>遲到</strong>與<strong>不遲到</strong>兩種</p>\n<p><strong>遲到</strong>的狀態表示<strong>E</strong>，發生的機率為<strong>0.5</strong></p>\n<p><strong>不遲到</strong>的狀態表示<strong>A</strong>，發生的機率為<strong>0.5</strong></p>\n<p>E—>E：今天<strong>遲到</strong>而且明天<strong>遲到</strong>，機率為<strong>0.3</strong></p>\n<p>E—>A: 今天<strong>遲到</strong>，明天<strong>不遲到</strong>，機率為<strong>0.7</strong></p>\n<p>A—>E：今天<strong>不遲到</strong>，明天<strong>遲到</strong>，機率為<strong>0.4</strong></p>\n<p>A—>A：今天<strong>不遲到</strong>而且明天<strong>不遲到</strong>，機率為<strong>0.6</strong></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"JS實作部份：\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/03/08/MarkovChain#JS實作部份：\"></a>JS實作部份：</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>主要分成2支檔案，模組化檔案一支，主程式一支</li>\n<li>出勤狀態圖<strong>模組化</strong>如下所示：</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 狀態機率： P(E) = 0.5, P(A) = 0.5</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 轉移機率： P(x => y)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//遲到的狀態表示E，發生的機率為0.5</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//不遲到的狀態表示A，發生的機率為0.5</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//E—>E：今天遲到而且明天遲到，機率為0.3</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//E—>A: 今天遲到，明天不遲到，機率為0.7</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//A—>E：今天不遲到，明天遲到，機率為0.4</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//A—>A：今天不遲到而且明天不遲到，機率為0.6</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> P = {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'E'</span>: <span class=\"number\">0.5</span>, <span class=\"string\">'A'</span>: <span class=\"number\">0.5</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'E=>E'</span>: <span class=\"number\">0.3</span>, <span class=\"string\">'E=>A'</span>: <span class=\"number\">0.7</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'A=>E'</span>: <span class=\"number\">0.4</span>, <span class=\"string\">'A=>A'</span>: <span class=\"number\">0.6</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">module</span>.exports = P<span class=\"comment\">//輸出模組</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>將模組化的檔案引入到<strong>主程式</strong>中</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> P = <span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">'./prob'</span>)<span class=\"comment\">//把模組引入</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">markov</span>(<span class=\"params\">status</span>) </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> p = P[status[<span class=\"number\">0</span>]]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i < status.length; i++) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> key = status[i - <span class=\"number\">1</span>] + <span class=\"string\">'=>'</span> + status[i]</span><br><span class=\"line\">        p = p * P[key]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> p</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> status = [<span class=\"string\">'E'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'A'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'E'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'E'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'A'</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">\"p=%j=%f\"</span>, status, markov(status))</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>主管預計小楨下星期出勤狀況會<strong>發生的機率</strong>如下: <font color=\"red\">0.293999</font></li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HUMARZt.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><strong>資料來源：</strong><br>\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A9%AC%E5%B0%94%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%AB%E9%93%BE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/马尔可夫链</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A9%AC%E5%B0%94%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%AB%E9%93%BE#/media/File:Markovkate_01.svg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/马尔可夫链#/media/File:Markovkate_01.svg</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://ccckmit.wikidot.com/ai:markov\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://ccckmit.wikidot.com/ai:markov</a></p>\n</body></html>","prev":{"title":"[正則表達式](一) ","link":"2020/03/22/RegExp-1"},"next":{"title":"[CodingStyle]命名規則","link":"2020/02/29/CodingStyle-命名規則"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/03/08/MarkovChain/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"淺談-馬可夫鏈-Markov-Chain","index":"1","children":[{"title":"","id":"原理：","index":"1.1"},{"title":"","id":"JS實作部份：","index":"1.2"}]}]}